						               													<description>A card game about the Cold War, an era dominated by the rivalries between the USA, their allies, and the USSR - between Cowboys and Commies. An era constantly on the verge of nuclear catastrophe.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Cowboys &amp;amp; Commies is a fast-paced card game for 2-4 players. During your turn you're playing a leader of one of the faction (Cowboys, Commies, Resistance or Dictators) and use their unique abilities to hinder you opponents and accumulate power. Each of the abilities are a reflection of the historical figure you're playing!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Each round is modified with an event. For example Chernobyl Disaster is a very bad news for the Commie cards in the game and the players must play accordingly.&amp;#10; After you win a round, you collect the event and you need 2 to win the entire game!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the designer&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
